race.comment: BUZZARD ZORRO (1) was a last start winner (16.24) from Box 5 at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Sure to prove hard to beat. NITRO VENOM (8) boasts a consistent overall record including six wins from 23 starts, the latest winning (16.15) over 278m at this track. Goes well from this draw. Looks suited and expected to run well. GET ON BOARD (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 278m behind Fay (16.64) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Expected to give a good account. HOW WE GO (3) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.
